      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASCEND JACARANDA (2) has a strong record this track and trip with five wins and four placings from 11 starts. Placed last time (26.59) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing third and beaten 6 lengths. Looks well placed and should feature. JAKE'S DESIRE (7) struggled in tougher grade last start at this track, but prior to that won comfortably by 4 lengths at this track (18.64) beating Time For Tea in a Grade 5 on May 27. Has the ability to give this a shake. IRINKA FRED (6) found the frame for the second consecutive time when narrowly beaten into second last time out (18.81) over 330m at this track. Expected to do much better this time. ALLERGY FREE (8) is always a threat when he draws this box.",
